net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.constrained

Class ConstrainedPAES

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.MOStrategy
      • net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.PAES
        • net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.constrained.ConstrainedPAES
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, net.sf.jclec.IConfigure, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC

    public class ConstrainedPAES
extends PAES
    A PAES strategy for problems with constraints. This class configures a constrained individual comparator that establishes the dominance criterion between feasible and infeasible individuals.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    PAES, ConstrainedComparator, IConstrained, Serialized Form

        public void createSolutionComparator(java.util.Comparator<net.sf.jclec.IFitness>[] components)
